  {
    "hotel_id": "8740480",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/hanoian-central-hotel-spa/hotel/hanoi-vn.html",
    "name": "Hanoian Central Hotel & Spa",
    "detail": "This hotel is in a convenient location in Hanoi. Its but a 5 minute walk to the Don Xuan Wholesale Market if you want to get bargain price goods and but a 15 minute walk to the Lake area and Hanoi's St Joseph Cathedral. But what sets this hotel apart is the small gestures of hospitality they gave my family on our visit. They arranged for us to get a better & larger room for our extra companion at a lower cost; They made sure to ask our inputs & comments on the tours we booked via the hotel each day and best of all they made sure to pack us a delicious & nutritious breakfast since we are unable to avail of it due to our early morning flight home. All this gestures might be small in nature but this is what truly matters and sets them apart from other hotels in Hanoi. Thank you to Molly, Ann and Elsa and the other staff of Hanoian Central for making our vacation in Hanoi a truly wonderful stay. You truly deserve a 5/5 star rating. ",
